headline: The RITZ Brand Partners with Feeding America® and Walmart to Fight Hunger
summary: The RITZ brand announced today the next chapter in a longstanding partnership with Feeding America®, the largest domestic hunger-relief organization in the country, to support people facing hunger through the Walmart "Fight Hunger. Spark Change." campaign.
